title: Burlingame Classic
posting_body: ['A Burlingame Classic Home with hardwood floors.', ' Formal living room with fireplace.', 'Formal dining room.', ' Remodeled kitchen with new cabinets and stone countertops.', ' New stainless steel gas stove and refrigerator.', ' Main bedroom has an  attached sunroom.', ' Second bedroom has two closets with new sliding doors.', ' Bathroom between the bedrooms is remodeled with tile tub shower and tile floor.', ' Third floor room perfect for a home office, study, playroom or library with wood floor and built-in shelves.', ' Basement has a half bath.', ' New washer and dryer.', ' It is carpeted and can be used as a family room, playroom or office.', ' One car garage that opens at both ends.', 'The backyard has new cement patio ready for a BBQ and planting area for a little garden.', ' Double pane windows.', 'The house is set back from the El Camino with a nice redwood garden.', ' The house is located close to shops and restaurants on Broadway.', '  Close to Caltrain, Bart and Caltrans.', ' 10 Min by car to SFO.', 'No smoking', 'Small dog OK with approval and extra Pet Deposit  No cats', 'Rent $4750 Security Deposit $4750 One year lease', '1041 El Camino Real, Burlingame']
